Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是平凡无奇的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定也有着不可告人的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.15,0:21:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有着向谁都无法倾诉的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.58,0:21:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:09.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢雾君 到底发生了什么……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.08,0:21:10.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是一开学就缺席……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了不知道了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.61,0:21:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问……
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.59,0:21:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是罪恶的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.93,0:21:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个眼镜妹爱上我了吧
