Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 你就不能用日语说话吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论是他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都隐藏着不同的秘密
